lert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Change or control Snow Snow character.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Change the color of the snow which suits on your site.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Super lightweight and easy to use.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Control number of maximum and active Flakes.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Allows snow to move dynamically with the wind, relative to the mouse&#8217;s X (left/right) coordinates.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Allows the snow to stick to the bottom of the window.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Control  Animation Interval.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Stops the snow effect when the browser window goes out of focus.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Support Melt and Twinkle  Effect.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Joomla 3.8 Ready.</div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-eye\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Product Screenshot</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n        <a href=\"https://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/snow_fall_new_demo.png\" target=\"_blank\"><br />\n            <img class=\"product-img\" src=\"https://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/snow_fall_new_demo.png\" alt=\"Product Image\"><br